Be sure J9600 metal plate is in place and check left/right connections.

title: 820-00923 NAND missing
message:
Check SSD basic signals; SSD_BOOT_LB_L, SSD_PWR_EN_LB_L, STORAGE_LB_EN, SSD_RESET_LB_L, SSD_PCIE_CLKREO_LB_L, LPSR_EN_LB_L.
If possible check 100MHz SSD clock with o-scope, or frequency meter.
